Package com.camerontec.catalys.core.session.inboundvalidation

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IFieldValidator
    Objects implementing this interface provide extra incoming message validation which is tag specific.
    IInboundMessageIntegrityChecker
    Performs basic low level integrity checking on an input message prior to detailed parsing of the message from its raw form (as returned by IFIXMessageSpecifics.getRawInMessage()).
    IInboundValidator
    Objects implementing this interface provide incoming FIX message validation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InboundFixMessageIntegrityChecker
    Performs FIX message integrity checking on inbound messages.
    InboundValidationDialects
    Provides a wrapper around a map of InboundValidationDialect values.
    InboundValidator
    Inbound message validator for header and footer
    InboundValidatorFactory
    Factory to create inbound message validators.
    NullMessageIntegrityChecker
    Null implementation of IInboundMessageIntegrityChecker.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    InboundValidationDialect
    Enumerates all dialects which affect inbound FIX message validation.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InboundValidationException
    Exception thrown when inbound message validation fails
